SELECT analysis_name, analysis_date FROM data_analysis;
SELECT u.username, d.data_source_name FROM users u JOIN data_sources d ON u.user_id = d.data_source_id;
SELECT a.analysis_id, a.analysis_name, u.username, d.data_source_name FROM data_analysis a JOIN users u ON a.user_id = u.user_id JOIN data_sources d ON a.data_source_id = d.data_source_id;

SELECT * FROM projects;
SELECT project_id, project_name FROM projects;
SELECT * FROM datasets;
SELECT dataset_id, dataset_name, size_in_mb FROM datasets;
SELECT * FROM models;
SELECT model_id, model_name, accuracy FROM models;
SELECT * FROM predictions;
SELECT prediction_id, project_id, model_id, prediction_value FROM predictions;
SELECT p.project_name, pr.prediction_value FROM projects p JOIN predictions pr ON p.project_id = pr.project_id;
SELECT d.dataset_name, m.model_name FROM datasets d JOIN models m ON d.dataset_id = m.model_id;
SELECT p.project_name, m.model_name, pr.prediction_value FROM projects p JOIN predictions pr ON p.project_id = pr.project_id JOIN models m ON pr.model_id = m.model_id;

SELECT p.project_name, d.dataset_name, m.model_name, pr.prediction_value FROM projects p JOIN predictions pr ON p.project_id = pr.project_id JOIN datasets d ON pr.dataset_id = d.dataset_id JOIN models m ON pr.model_id = m.model_id;
SELECT project_name, COUNT(prediction_id) AS prediction_count FROM projects LEFT JOIN predictions ON projects.project_id = predictions.project_id GROUP BY project_name;
SELECT model_name, AVG(accuracy) AS avg_accuracy FROM models GROUP BY model_name;

SELECT project_name, MAX(accuracy) AS max_accuracy FROM projects JOIN predictions ON projects.project_id = predictions.project_id JOIN models ON predictions.model_id = models.model_id GROUP BY project_name;
SELECT project_name, COUNT(model_id) AS model_count FROM projects JOIN predictions ON projects.project_id = predictions.project_id GROUP BY project_name;

SELECT project_name, SUM(size_in_mb) AS total_size FROM projects JOIN predictions ON projects.project_id = predictions.project_id JOIN datasets ON predictions.dataset_id = datasets.dataset_id GROUP BY project_name;
SELECT DISTINCT project_name FROM projects;
SELECT project_name, prediction_value FROM projects JOIN predictions ON projects.project_id = predictions.project_id WHERE prediction_value LIKE 'positive%';
